attys-ep
-----------

This program performs averaging over repetitive stimuli. It
works on continous data such as visually evoked potentials and
also on discrete events such as spikes. Its main application
is for visually evoked potentials.

This program uses the Attys (www.attys.tech) to measure the
(EEG-) signal.

